org.ica.uiElements

Class AddNewEquation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Dialog
      • org.ica.uiElements.AddNewEquation

  • public class AddNewEquation
extends org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Dialog
    This class creates a dialog for manipulating Equation objects, The first constructor creates a new Equation object, the second constructor allows the user to modify an already existent Equation object.
    Author:
    Salim Ahmed
